{"tid":1438400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Router Block IP 令家人免被洗腦","createTime":"2019-08-09T18:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:12:16.000Z","uid":55597,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9096f15b0eacb8d8d25506887597d15a456c83","tid":1438400,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/cSG84HL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FcSG84HL.png&h=5a90c93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nping <a href=\"http://www.hk01.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=c889fa16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hk01.com</a> 搵佢個 IP<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/3G9En9j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F3G9En9j.png&h=871f2935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去 Firewall 設定<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/BEBhLo7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FBEBhLo7.png&h=0c302461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去 IPv4 Rules<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/pHBqOOH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FpHBqOOH.png&h=c8a984d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啟動 filter 使用 deny rules<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/KQi7MKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FKQi7MKu.png&h=0f5a3c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource IP 設定為區域 LAN<br />\n如果你個 IP 係 192.168.0.1 咁就設定做 192.168.0.0-192.168.0.255<br />\nDestination IP 設定為廣播 WAN<br />\n因為 hk01 IP 係 13.22.161.* 咁就設定做 13.22.161.0-13.22.161.255<br />\n然後 Apply<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/HLAXhzI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FHLAXhzI.png&h=1f5d4ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後 Save<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/yHqja8U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FyHqja8U.png&h=aa77656a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSaving<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/yC69jzA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FyC69jzA.png&h=186cd034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大約60秒後再 ping <a href=\"http://www.hk01.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=c889fa16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hk01.com</a> 應該會失敗<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/TlSOPfX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FTlSOPfX.png&h=064b4c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWeb Browser 都應該上唔到<br />\n<br />\n我用緊 DIR-818LW<br />\n用 Website Filter 唔可以 block HTTPS 網頁，所有改用 Firewall block<br />\n其他牌子點 set 要等其他人<br />\n<br />\n另外咪用中國公司既 Router<br />\n如果就係用緊 TP-Link, 華為 Router ，請盡快改用其他非中國公司既 Router 例如 Cisco, D-Link, NetGear"},{"pid":"c8c0aec7f23321f27e37ead1780a6629c4bae0db","tid":1438400,"uid":89857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f9096f15b0eacb8d8d25506887597d15a456c83","tid":1438400,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/cSG84HL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FcSG84HL.png&h=5a90c93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nping <a href=\"http://www.hk01.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=c889fa16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hk01.com</a> 搵佢個 IP<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/3G9En9j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F3G9En9j.png&h=871f2935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去 Firewall 設定<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/BEBhLo7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FBEBhLo7.png&h=0c302461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去 IPv4 Rules<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/pHBqOOH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna